I am ashamed to be a part of Hollywood: Charlize Theron.
Charlize Theron has slammed Hollywood for not giving women an opportunity to work with higher budgets.The 41-year-old actor said she is ashamed of the film industry, reported Variety.Charlize Theron arrives at the Dior Cruise Show at the Upper Las Virgenes Canyon Open Space Preserve.
							(Willy Sanjuan/Invision/AP)
						I am ashamed that Im part of an industry that has never allowed a woman to work with a budget higher (than Wonder Woman).Thats so caveman-like. I am always hoping that this is the movie thats going to change it, Theron said. The actor will next be seen in Atomic Blonde, due out on August 28.Follow @htshowbiz for more